<i>noun</i>: 비참 [비ː참], 불행 [불행] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비참 [비ː참]</dt><br>
<dd>misery; wretchedness; distress</dd><br>
<dd>견딜 수 없을 정도로 슬프고 끔찍함.</dd><br>
<dd>An unbearably sad and dreadful feeling.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불행 [불행]</dt><br>
<dd>1. unhapiness; misery</dd><br>
<dd>행복하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of not being happy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unhappiness; difficulty; misery</dd><br>
<dd>운이 없음. 좋지 않은 일을 당함.</dd><br>
<dd>Lack of luck, or experiencing undesirable events.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>